Package diceTools.function

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Append<T>
    Function to append values to a List.
    Burst
    Function to replace values in a List with each value from a DiceRollMap to generate a DicePoolMap
    Count
    Function to count Integer's in a List.
    DiscardN<T>
    Function to discard some values in a List.
    Explode
    Function to repeatedly apply Burst.apply(List) to a List<DiceNumber>
    KeepN<T>
    Function to keep some values in a List, and discard the rest.
    Replace<T>
    Function to replace some values in a list with others.
